targets.query: SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_hostdomclient" WITH KEY = "hostname" WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^Cluster-34$/)
SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_virtualmachine" WITH KEY = "uuid"  WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/)
SELECT mean("used_latest") * (100 / mean("capacity_latest"))  FROM "vsphere_datastore_disk" WHERE ("source" =~ /^$datastore$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT (mean("total_capacity_byte") - mean("free_capacity_byte")) / mean("total_capacity_byte") * 100 FROM "vsphere_vsan_summary" WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_diskgroup" WITH KEY = "devicename"  WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/)
SHOW TAG VALUES CARDINALITY FROM "vsphere_vsan_performance_capacitydisk" WITH KEY = "devicename"  WHERE ("clustername" =~ /^$cluster$/)
